						<summary>

						<p>This is a fragment of an inscription dated in the 11th year of some king whose name is lost. The writing is of about the 10th Century A.D. Reference is made to an organisation of a district by name Aha-nāḍu, and also to the <hi rend="italic">ugachchar</hi> and <hi rend="italic">paṭṭuḍaiyār</hi> of the temple.</p>						

						</summary>
